Unlike prior surveys that focus on non-RL agentic RAG or general search agents, or on RL methods limited to building deep-research systems, 
our work uniquely unifies RL foundations with agentic search behavior, 
analyzing how RL benefits agentic search, how it optimizes search agents, and how such systems can be effectively evaluated.

